---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import LocalSEO from '../components/LocalSEO.astro';
import LocalServiceAreas from '../components/LocalServiceAreas.astro';
---

<Layout title="About PCFG Insurance Services - Veteran-Owned Agency in Parish, NY" description="Learn about PCFG Insurance Services, a veteran-owned insurance agency based in Parish, NY with over 5 years of experience serving businesses and families across 15 states. Founded in 2018 by Army veteran Liam O'Brien.">
  <LocalSEO pageName="About Us" pageDescription="Learn about our veteran-owned insurance agency based in Parish, NY" />
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About PCFG Insurance Services - Parish, NY</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          A veteran-owned insurance agency based in Parish, New York, dedicated to protecting what matters most to your business and family across 15 states since 2018.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Company Story -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Founded in Parish, New York with the principles of service, integrity, and excellence learned through military service, PCFG Insurance Services has been protecting businesses and families across 15 states since December 2018.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            As a veteran-owned agency headquartered in Central New York, we understand the importance of reliability, attention to detail, and going above and beyond for those we serve. These values guide everything we do, from providing personalized insurance solutions to delivering exceptional customer service across all our licensed states.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            Our mission is simple: to provide comprehensive insurance protection from our Parish, NY headquarters that gives our clients peace of mind across 15 states, allowing them to focus on what they do best – running their businesses and caring for their families.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/Liam.jpeg" alt="Liam O'Brien" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Liam O'Brien</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-600 font-semibold mb-4">Founder & President</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              U.S. Army Veteran with extensive experience in the insurance industry. Dedicated to serving the community with the same commitment to excellence learned in military service.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Licensed States Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Licensed Across 15 States from Our Parish, NY Headquarters</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          From our base in Parish, New York (Oswego County), PCFG Insurance Services is licensed to serve businesses and families across 15 states, bringing our expertise and personalized service to communities nationwide.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
        <LocalServiceAreas variant="grid" />
        
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Whether you're a small business owner, large corporation, or individual looking for personal insurance, we're here to serve you with the same level of excellence from our Parish, NY office across all our licensed states.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-navy-600 hover:bg-navy-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200">
            Get Your Free Quote Today
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- To Our Customers Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">To Our Customers</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            At PCFG Insurance Services, our relationship with you extends far beyond a simple transaction. We view ourselves as your trusted advisors and partners in protecting what matters most to you and your business.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Our commitment to you is built on three fundamental principles: transparency, expertise, and unwavering advocacy. We believe you deserve to understand exactly what you're purchasing, why it's important, and how it protects you. That's why we take the time to educate you about your coverage options and explain the details in plain language.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            When you work with PCFG Insurance Services, you're not just getting an insurance policy – you're gaining a dedicated team that will be there when you need us most. Whether you're filing a claim, need to make changes to your coverage, or simply have questions, we're here to help navigate the complexities of insurance on your behalf.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We understand that insurance can be complicated, and that's exactly why you need an experienced advocate in your corner. Our job is to make the complex simple, to ensure you have the right coverage at the right price, and to be your voice when dealing with insurance companies.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-navy-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-navy-600 mb-6">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium">
              "Your trust is something we never take for granted. It's earned through consistent service, honest communication, and always putting your interests first."
            </p>
            <p class="text-navy-600 font-semibold mt-4">— The PCFG Insurance Services Team</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Compensation Disclosure Link -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Transparency in Everything We Do</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              As part of our commitment to transparency, we want you to understand how we are compensated for our services. We believe this information helps you make informed decisions about your insurance purchases.
            </p>
            <a href="/compensation-disclosure" class="bg-navy-600 hover:bg-navy-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
              View Our Compensation Disclosure
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Mission & Values -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission & Values</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">The principles that guide our commitment to excellence</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-navy-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Integrity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We conduct business with honesty, transparency, and ethical practices in all our interactions.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-navy-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Service</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We serve our clients with dedication, putting their needs first and going above and beyond expectations.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-navy-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We strive for excellence in everything we do, continuously improving our services and expertise.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-navy-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Community</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We're committed to supporting and strengthening the communities we serve across all our licensed states.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Experience Timeline -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Building trust and serving our community since 2018</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-px h-full w-0.5 bg-gray-200"></div>
        
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-1 text-right pr-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">December 2018</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">PCFG Insurance Services founded with a commitment to serve the local business community with veteran values</p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-navy-600 rounded-full">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 pl-8"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-1 pr-8"></div>
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-navy-600 rounded-full">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 text-left pl-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2020</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Expanded services to include comprehensive employee benefits and group health insurance during challenging times</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-1 text-right pr-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2021</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Added cyber liability and technology insurance to meet evolving business needs in the digital age</p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-navy-600 rounded-full">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 pl-8"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-1 pr-8"></div>
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-navy-600 rounded-full">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 text-left pl-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2022</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Achieved recognition as a trusted workers' compensation specialist and expanded licensing to multiple states</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-1 text-right pr-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2024</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Celebrating over 5 years of protecting businesses and families across 15 states with continued growth and innovation</p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-navy-600 rounded-full">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 pl-8"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-navy-600">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Experience the PCFG Difference</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join hundreds of satisfied clients across 15 states who trust us to protect what matters most to their business and family.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-navy-600 hover:bg-gray-100 px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200">
          Get Your Free Quote
        </a>
        <a href="/services" class="border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-navy-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200">
          View Our Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>